Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN
DECLARE @String VARCHAR(100)
WHILE LEN(@StringInput) > 0 BEGIN SET @String = LEFT(@StringInput, ISNULL(NULLIF(CHARINDEX(',', @StringInput) - 1, -1), LEN(@StringInput))) SET @StringInput = SUBSTRING(@StringInput, ISNULL(NULLIF(CHARINDEX(',', @StringInput), 0), LEN(@StringInput)) + 1, LEN(@StringInput))
INSERT INTO @OutputTable ( [Value] ) VALUES ( @String ) END
RETURN END
